                <h4 class="title font-weight-semi-bold" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">What We Do</h4>
                <p class="font-weight-semi-bold" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">IN THE 21ST CENTURY, DATA IS KING.</p>
                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">We all have heared of the Golden Rule in the past…..it said “ one with the gold makes the rules’
