                <p class="font-weight-semi-bold" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">
                    THE ONE WITH THE DATA MAKES THE RULES
                </p>

                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">Our world has changed and data and the use of data rules. A search on the internet for the top 10 most valuable companies in the world will show 7 of the 10 are companies whose business models are hinged tightly around big data assimilation.</p>

                <p class="font-weight-semi-bold" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">
                    RETAIL IN AFRICA IS READY FOR DISRUPTION
                </p>

                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">The African retails space is still mostly brick and mortar with very little e-commerce penetration. Retailers have very little personal knowledge of their customers. This results in situations where all customers are treated the same. </p>

                <p class="mb-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">But we know not all customers are the same. Our wants and needs at the core differ…. Real Excellent Customer Experience can only be achieved when customers are served based on their core needs.</p>


                <h4 class="title font-weight-semi-bold" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">What We Do</h4>

                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-once="true"  data-aos-duration="800">RIFL Neo learns and aggregates customer bio data, purchase history, shopping psycology, social settings etc. to determine certain customer patterns. Every single data collected is securely logged and then analyzed to properly understand the customer’s current needs and projection made for FUTURE needs. </p>

